    "en": {
      "title": "Power cuts are reduced to one hour on weekends",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Janaka Rathnayake, its chairman, said today (2) that the Public Utilities Commission has given permission for power cuts from tomorrow (3rd) to 5th due to the shortage of fuel needed for power generation.",
        "Mr. Janaka Rathnayake further said that tomorrow and the next day (3rd and 4th) electricity will be cut for one hour only during the night time and next Saturday (5th) for two hours during the day and night time."
      ],
